. 그것은 미감정 상태일때 silver bell입니다.\"/>\n<link rel=\"image_src\" href=\"/images/6/65/Nethackwiki-logo.png\"/>\n<link rel=\"shortcut icon\" href=\"/images/6/64/Favicon.ico\"/>\n<link rel=\"search\" type=\"application/opensearchdescription+xml\" href=\"/opensearch_desc.php\" title=\"NetHackWiki\"/>\n<link rel=\"EditURI\" type=\"application/rsd+xml\" href=\"https://nethackwiki.com/api.php?action=rsd\"/>\n<link rel=\"canonical\" href=\"/wiki/Bell_of_Opening/ko\"/>\n<!--[if lt IE 9]><script src=\"/load.php?debug=false&amp;lang=en&amp;modules=html5shiv&amp;only=scripts&amp;skin=vector&amp;sync=1\"></script><![endif]-->\n</head>\n<body class=\"mediawiki ltr sitedir-ltr mw-hide-empty-elt ns-0 ns-subject page-Bell_of_Opening_ko rootpage-Bell_of_Opening skin-vector action-view\">\t\t<div id=\"mw-page-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"mw-head-base\" class=\"noprint\"></div>\n\t\t<div id=\"content\" class=\"mw-body\" role=\"main\">\n\t\t\t<a id=\"top\"></a>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"mw-indicators mw-body-content\">\n</div>\n<h1 id=\"firstHeading\" class=\"firstHeading\" lang=\"en\">Bell of Opening/ko</h1>\t\t\t<div id=\"bodyContent\" class=\"mw-body-content\">\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"siteSub\" class=\"noprint\">From NetHackWiki</div>\t\t\t\t<div id=\"contentSub\"><span class=\"subpages\">&lt; <a href=\"/wiki/Bell_of_Opening\" title=\"Bell of Opening\">Bell of Opening</a></span></div>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n\t\t\t\t<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#p-search\">Jump to search</a>\n\t\t\t\t<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\">\n<table class=\"prettytable\" style=\"margin: 0;\">\n<tbody><tr>\n<th colspan=\"2\"><span class=\"nhsym clr-lightgray\">(</span> <a href=\"/wiki/File:Bell_of_Opening.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Bell of Opening.png\" src=\"/images/5/54/Bell_of_Opening.png\" width=\"16\" height=\"16\" /></a>\n</th></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Name\n</th>\n<td>Bell of Opening\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Appearance\n</th>\n<td>silver bell\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Base price\n</th>\n<td>5000 <a href=\"/wiki/Zorkmid\" title=\"Zorkmid\">zm</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Weight\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Weight\" title=\"Weight\">10</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Material\n</th>\n<td><a href=\"/wiki/Silver\" title=\"Silver\">silver</a>\n</td></tr>\n<tr>\n<th>Monster use\n</th>\n<td><small><i>Will not be used by monsters.</i></small>\n</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</div>\n<p><b>개방의 종</b>은 <a href=\"/wiki/Invocation\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Invocation\">의식</a>에 필요한 아이템중 하나입니다. 그것은 미감정 상태일때 <b>silver bell</b>입니다.\n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><input type=\"checkbox\" role=\"button\" id=\"toctogglecheckbox\" class=\"toctogglecheckbox\" style=\"display:none\" /><div class=\"toctitle\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\"><h2>Contents</h2><span class=\"toctogglespan\"><label class=\"toctogglelabel\" for=\"toctogglecheckbox\"></label></span></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#.EC.83.9D.EC.84.B1\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">생성</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#.ED.9A.A8.EA.B3.BC\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">효과</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#.EC.A0.84.EB.9E.B5\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">전략</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#.EC.8B.A0.ED.99.94\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">신화</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Encyclopedia_entry\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Encyclopedia entry</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h2><span id=\"생성\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".EC.83.9D.EC.84.B1\">생성</span></h2>\n<p>그것은 <a href=\"/wiki/Quest\" title=\"Quest\">퀘스트</a> 도중에 만나는 <a href=\"/wiki/Unique_item\" title=\"Unique item\">unique item</a>입니다 (당신의 직업 <a href=\"/wiki/Quest_artifact\" title=\"Quest artifact\">퀘스트 아티팩트</a>와 함께 옵니다)\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"효과\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".ED.9A.A8.EA.B3.BC\">효과</span></h2>\n<p>충전량이 있을때 적용하면, <a href=\"/wiki/Wand_of_secret_door_detection/ko\" title=\"Wand of secret door detection/ko\">비밀문 탐지의 지팡이</a>처럼, 그것은 숨겨진 문과 <a href=\"/wiki/Trap\" title=\"Trap\">함정</a>을 8제곱 반지름의 시각적 범위에서 탐지할 것입니다. (<a href=\"/wiki/Magic_portal\" title=\"Magic portal\">마법 포탈</a> 포함) 그리고 삼켜졌을때, 당신을 뱉어내게 만들기도 합니다. (<a href=\"/wiki/Wand_of_opening\" title=\"Wand of opening\">개방의 완드</a>처럼). 만약 축복받았다면, 그것은 추가적으로 사물들을 열 것입니다. (문, 상자, 도개교 등) 만약 저주받았고 충전된 상태라면, 그것은 이러한 효과중 아무것도 없을 것이고; 그것은 대신 <a href=\"/wiki/Book_of_the_dead#Raising_the_dead\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Book of the dead\">사자를 깨울 것이며</a> (하지만 시체를 부활시키지는 않을 것입니다) 그리고 근처의 몬스터를 깨웁니다.<sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> 충전되지 않았다면, 그것은 평범하지만 부서지지 않는 <a href=\"/wiki/Bell\" title=\"Bell\">종</a>처럼 작용할 것입니다. 삼켜지지 않았거나 충전되지 않은 개방의 종을 의식에 사용하려고 시도할 때 저주가 없는 개방 벨을 성공적으로 사용하면 벨을 완전히 식별할 수 있습니다.\n</p><p>종은 3의 충전량을 가지고 시작하며,<sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> 최대 5까지 충전할수 있습니다. 만약 그것들을 다 써버리면, <a href=\"/wiki/Invocation\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Invocation\">의식</a>을 하기 전에 그것을 충전해야 할 것입니다.\n</p><p>개방의 종은 <a href=\"/wiki/Container\" title=\"Container\">container</a> 안에 넣을수 없으며, 다른 의식용 아티팩트처럼 파괴할수도 없습니다.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"전략\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".EC.A0.84.EB.9E.B5\">전략</span></h2>\n<p>의식 이외에도 추가로, <a href=\"/wiki/Moloch%27s_Sanctum\" title=\"Moloch&#39;s Sanctum\">Moloch's Sanctum</a>의 사원 벽에 있는 숨겨진 문을 찾는데에 유용합니다.\n</p><p>종을 장착한 상태로 적을 때리는 것은 <a href=\"/wiki/Silver#Silver_damage\" title=\"Silver\">은 피해</a>를 줄수 있지만, <a href=\"/wiki/Weaponless\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Weaponless\">weaponless</a> 컨덕트를 깨트리지 않습니다.\n</p>\n<h2><span id=\"신화\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\".EC.8B.A0.ED.99.94\">신화</span></h2>\n<p>벨, 책, 촛불은 가톨릭의 탈교 의식입니다.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Encyclopedia_entry\">Encyclopedia entry</span></h2><div class=\"nhencyclopedia\">\n<div class=\"poem\">\n<p>\"A bell, book and candle job.\"<br />\nThe Bursar sighed.  \"We tried that, Archchancellor.\"<br />\nThe Archchancellor leaned towards him.<br />\n\"Eh?\" he said.<br />\n\"I _said_, we tried that Archchancellor,\" said the Bursar loudly, directing his voice at the old man's ear.  \"After dinner, you remember?  We used Humptemper's _Names of the Ants_ and rang Old Tom.\"*<br />\n\"Did we, indeed.  Worked, did it?\"<br />\n\"_No_, Archchancellor.\"<br />\n&#160;<br />\n* Old Tom was the single cracked bronze bell in the University bell tower.<br />\n</p>\n<div style=\"text-align:right\">[ Eric, by Terry Pratchett ] </div>\n</div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/wiki/Source:NetHack_3.4.3/apply.c#line812\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Source:NetHack 3.4.3/apply.c\">apply.c<span></span> in NetHack 3.4.3, line 812</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/wiki/Source:NetHack_3.4.3/makemon.c#line1029\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Source:NetHack 3.4.3/makemon.c\">makemon.c<span></span> in NetHack 3.4.3, line 1029</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/wiki/Source:NetHack_3.4.3/mkobj.c#line515\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Source:NetHack 3.4.3/mkobj.c\">mkobj.c<span></span> in NetHack 3.4.3, line 515</a>\n     </span>\n</li>\n</ol></div>\n<div style=\"display:none; right:10px; padding-bottom: 17px\" class=\"metadata topicon nopopups\"><div style=\"margin-top: -10px\"><a href=\"/wiki/NetHackWiki:Next_version\" title=\"This article may require revision for the next version of NetHack. Click here for more information.\"><img alt=\"This article may require revision for the next version of NetHack. Click here for more information.\" src=\"/images/b/b0/Nh343-icon.png\" width=\"32\" height=\"32\" /></a></div></div>\n<div class=\"todo\">\n<p><b>This page may need to be updated for the <a href=\"/wiki/Current_version\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Current version\">current version</a> of <i>NetHack</i>.</b>\n</p><p>It may contain text specific to <a href=\"/wiki/NetHack_3.4.3\" title=\"NetHack 3.4.3\">NetHack 3.4.3</a>. Information on this page may be out of date.\n</p><p><b>Editors:</b> After reviewing this page and making necessary edits, please change the {{nethack-343}} tag to the current version's tag or {{noversion}} as appropriate.\n</p>\n</div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20240926182540\nCache expiry: 604800\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.027 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.037 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 384/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 1865/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4442/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 1203/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 9/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 1/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1707/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%   22.190      1 -total\n 32.82%    7.282      3 Template:Refsrc\n 22.96%    5.095      1 Template:Tool\n 22.93%    5.088      1 Template:Nethack-343\n 15.68% 